header.gameNote: PAC-12 MEN'S TOURNAMENT PRES. BY NEW YORK LIFE - QUARTERFINAL

videos.description: Dejounte Murray leads the Washington fast break and throws the lob up to Marquese Chriss who tries to bring down the basket with a huge alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Chriss showing huge postseason hops with alley-oop dunk

videos.description: 1H (18:15) WASH Andrew Andrews lobs it over to Marquese Chriss on transition for the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: A. Andrews lobs it over to M. Chriss on transition for the two-handed slam.

D. Murray steal, almost loses the ball on the fastbreak but manages to make the layup.
